  personSpokenTo: {fileID: 11400000, guid: 08a894b9b170bd4408c3738b6b563b07, type: 2}
  delayBetweenMessages: 2
  lines:
  - "I can never work as hard as you do though\u2026"
  - You do too much for me please, I can always work part time to help pay for university
  bridgeAfterMessages: 1
  bridgeResponse1: "You\u2019re selflessness is just like that of your mother\u2019s,
    I can only imagine how proud she\u2019d be seeing how you turned out. But don\u2019t
    worry about me, I don\u2019t want to change a thing about my life. Have a good
    nights rest, I look forward to seeing you when you\u2019re back."
